HEADWORD: Zoochemistry
<hw>Zo`o*chem"is*try</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Zoo-</ets> + <ets>chemistry</ets>.]</ety> <def>Animal
chemistry; particularly, the description of the chemical compounds
entering into the composition of the animal body, in distinction from
<xex>biochemistry</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
